    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/77616daa6aa83a1d016f7850e3f78205.poster.avif?t=1739554433\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/77616daa6aa83a1d016f7850e3f78205.webm?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/77616daa6aa83a1d016f7850e3f78205.mp4?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Linked is a short puzzle platformer experience made in a 72 hour gamejam with a cozy soundtrack, and short, yet sweet story! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/2989c951cd6d7024775011c4227a1268.poster.avif?t=1739554433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/2989c951cd6d7024775011c4227a1268.webm?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/2989c951cd6d7024775011c4227a1268.mp4?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore space, the deep ocean, and past ages in short, yet sweet levels spanning across all three. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/d5c0599bb16cfcd35f0370fbd5f6a8b9.poster.avif?t=1739554433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/d5c0599bb16cfcd35f0370fbd5f6a8b9.webm?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/d5c0599bb16cfcd35f0370fbd5f6a8b9.mp4?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you'll discover new and interesting ways to beat levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The average playtime is no longer than 15 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/ef800f04269d91dc8edcba6ec3001b2e.poster.avif?t=1739554433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/ef800f04269d91dc8edcba6ec3001b2e.webm?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310830/extras/ef800f04269d91dc8edcba6ec3001b2e.mp4?t=1739554433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEV NOTE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is our first game that we decide to publish, so we really hope you all enjoy, and are excited to see what we bring in the future!</p>",
